
    ● Selenium IDE is
    implemented as
    Chrome and Firefox extension,
    and allows us to record,
    edit, and debug tests.
    ● Selenium RC
    is to write automated
    web application
    UI tests in any programming language
    ● Selenium WebDriver
    interface,
    executes our tests
    against different browsers

    ● Selenium GRID
    runs our tests
    on different
    machines against
    different browsers in parallel.